headline: Expeditors International Earnings Preview: What to Expect
summary: Expeditors is scheduled to release its Q4 results next month, and analysts are projecting a double-digit profit decline for the upcoming quarter.

headline: 1 Profitable Stock Worth Your Attention and 2 That Underwhelm
summary: Not all profitable companies are built to last - some rely on outdated models or unsustainable advantages. Just because a business is in the green today doesn’t mean it will thrive tomorrow.
